short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Budweiser Canada has created a special tool to add a little extra Whassup! to your day.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Whassup It" is a browser extension that converts any hello’s on a webpage into Whassup. But it doesn’t stop at hello’s, lots of other simple greetings can be converted into Whassup. Hi. Hey. G’Day. Howdy. And many more!
 
.
